Title name:

Application Development Code Snippet Generator Agent

Problem Statement:

Developers often need quick code snippets or templates for common programming tasks. Searching documentation or forums can be time-consuming. An Al agent that generates relevant code snippets based on natural language requests can speed up development.

Steps:

Use a Large Language Model to interpret developer requests.

Generate Python code snippets or templates for common tasks.

Allow iterative refinement through conversational interaction.

Provide explanations for generated code.

Data Requirements:

No external data required; rely on pre-trained LLM capabilities.

Expected Output:

Python code snippets and explanations delivered in text format via a conversational interface.
